Well, in a sense I don't say looking after but if there was any help needed - what I mean - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1514159\charrsid10316288 it}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288  - it would be done. Oh yes. Oh yes, yes. Oh yes.
