Well, I was going you see to - as I said I was going to Plas Lewis school now. Well I got up later of course when I was going to Llan, a smaller boy, but she'd get us up and our breakfast would be there ready for us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 Who would have breakfast now then?
