My mother - wouldn't be able when - she - she wasn't strong you see, my mother would have - she was very fond after of - you know, hav
ing - I - I suppose you call it now, it - it was like sour milk, and she would - yes, and she, yes, buttermilk, but she was making cheese out of it. Yes. She used to do a lot of that herself you see. Because my mother could - yes. Through a cloth. Yes. Ye
s.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 Very nourishing?
