Oh well, he'd have his dinner then you see. Yes. What we call broth. Broth. Lot of broth, yes. There'd be parsley and - leeks, and of course the top of it would be - all \{BLANK\} And then - potatoes and bit of meat after it. It was good -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 A lot of it you used to have?
