Well my hobbies then when I was at school, when I come from school was got to this farmer. I was - I wanted to go there. I was very - very fond of horses, still am, very fond of horses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 Did you keep any pets?
