Oh no. No, I didn't - didn't do that. No, it was - to rob a nest in those days and if caught - we were all - they thought it was terrible to rob a nest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 Did you do any gardening or anything like that?
