Yes. When I started to work - out of - two shillings a day, twelve shillings, well I wasn't having twelve shillings to go home. I was having - shilling. My pocket money was for the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 You gave your wages all to your mother did you?
