Oh yes. And - then I had - an increase in my wage, from two shillings to half a crown a day. And they ros
e - my mother - my mother rose then - my pocket money from shilling to one and three. And - then I - as I'd have an increase it was increasing a bit, but I never had a lot of money and - well of course - a lot of money then you see would be - nothing at a
ll today would it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 You gave your wages to your mother?
