Well - yes - I - shall I - I've had regrets, because - the opportunities are on peoples laps today, which were not in those days. That's the onl
y thing. But I - the opportunities that were in those days of course I was very pleased about and very good for, but I often think how things are today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid396929 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4345113 WP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4930995\charrsid10316288 Oh definitely. Definitely.
